---
layout: base.njk
title: Profile
---

<div class="profile-container">
  <!-- Sticky Sidebar Navigation -->
  <aside class="sidebar-nav">
    <nav class="sidebar-menu">
      <a href="#journey" class="sidebar-link active" data-section="journey">My Journey</a>
      <a href="#experience" class="sidebar-link" data-section="experience">Experience</a>
      <a href="#education" class="sidebar-link" data-section="education">Education</a>
      <a href="#licenses" class="sidebar-link" data-section="licenses">Licenses & Certifications</a>
      <a href="#volunteering" class="sidebar-link" data-section="volunteering">Volunteering</a>
      <a href="#awards" class="sidebar-link" data-section="awards">Honors & Awards</a>
    </nav>
  </aside>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="profile-content">

    <!-- My Journey (map + summary) -->
    <section id="journey" class="profile-section">
      <h2>My Journey</h2>
      <div id="map-section">
        <div id="map" style="width:100%;height:360px;border-radius:8px;"></div>
        <div id="journey-summary" style="margin-top:1rem;display:flex;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
            <p>Curiosity has driven my journey from the start. I grew up taking hardware and software apart just to see how they worked, which shaped me into a creative, systems-oriented problem solver with a relentless taste for experimentation.</p>
            <p>One project felt like unlocking a cheat code in a video game: building a capacitive touch panel controller entirely from scratch. Using a PIC18F microcontroller, I wrote every line of firmware to drive the FocalTech FT5X06 chip, bringing multi-touch gestures to life on a 4.3" Newhaven TFT display. Watching my code respond instantly to finger swipes was pure exhilaration‚Äîlike beating a boss level after weeks of grinding.</p>
            <p>That same thrill carried me into enterprise systems, where I built VB.NET applications to track RMAs at a manufacturing firm in Elgin, IL, opening the door to financial platforms and business processes. Since then, I've mastered how data, workflows, and people intersect across complex organizations.</p>
            <p>My focus has since expanded‚Äîbridging functional needs, technical architecture, and user experience with AI, machine learning, and intelligent automation. Today, I'm chasing that same video game rush: creating financial and operational systems that are efficient, intuitive, resilient, and genuinely inspiring to use.</p>
          </div>
  
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Leaflet CSS/JS and map initialization -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
      <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
      <script>
        (function(){
          // Initialize map centered on USA
          const map = L.map('map').setView([39.8283, -98.5795], 4);
          L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {
            attribution: '&copy; OpenStreetMap',
            minZoom: 2,
            maxZoom: 19
          }).addTo(map);

          // Companies data from journey.json
          const companies = [
            {% for c in journey %}
            {
              id: "{{ c.id | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              company: "{{ c.company | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              location: "{{ c.location | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              lat: {{ c.lat | default('null') }},
              lon: {{ c.lon | default('null') }}
            }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          ];

          // Schools data from education.json
          const schools = [
            {% for edu in education %}
            {
              id: "{{ edu.id | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              name: "{{ edu.school | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              location: "{{ edu.location | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              degree: "{{ edu.degree | default('') | replace('"', '\\"') }}",
              lat: {{ edu.lat | default('null') }},
              lon: {{ edu.lon | default('null') }}
            }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          ];

          // Red marker icon for schools
          const redIcon = L.icon({
            iconUrl: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pointhi/leaflet-color-markers/master/img/marker-icon-red.png',
            shadowUrl: 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.9.4/images/marker-shadow.png',
            iconSize: [25, 41],
            iconAnchor: [12, 41],
            popupAnchor: [1, -34],
            shadowSize: [41, 41]
          });

          // Blue marker icon (default)
          const blueIcon = L.icon({
            iconUrl: 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pointhi/leaflet-color-markers/master/img/marker-icon-blue.png',
            shadowUrl: 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.9.4/images/marker-shadow.png',
            iconSize: [25, 41],
            iconAnchor: [12, 41],
            popupAnchor: [1, -34],
            shadowSize: [41, 41]
          });

          // Add company markers (blue)
          for (const c of companies) {
            if (c.lat && c.lon) {
              const lat = parseFloat(c.lat);
              const lon = parseFloat(c.lon);
              if (!isNaN(lat) && !isNaN(lon)) {
                const marker = L.marker([lat, lon], { icon: blueIcon }).addTo(map);
                marker.bindPopup('<strong>' + c.company + '</strong><br/>' + (c.location || ''));
                continue;
              }
            }
            // Fallback: add to list if coordinates missing
            const li = document.createElement('li');
            li.textContent = c.company + ' ‚Äî ' + (c.location || 'Unknown');
            document.getElementById('journey-list').appendChild(li);
          }

          // Add school markers (red)
          for (const s of schools) {
            if (s.lat && s.lon) {
              const lat = parseFloat(s.lat);
              const lon = parseFloat(s.lon);
              if (!isNaN(lat) && !isNaN(lon)) {
                const marker = L.marker([lat, lon], { icon: redIcon }).addTo(map);
                marker.bindPopup('<strong>' + s.name + '</strong><br/>' + (s.degree || ''));
                continue;
              }
            }
            // Fallback: add to list if coordinates missing
            const li = document.createElement('li');
            li.textContent = s.name + ' ‚Äî ' + (s.location || 'Unknown');
            document.getElementById('journey-list').appendChild(li);
          }
        })();
      </script>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;justify-content:center;">
        <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u5v1vZr6F9k" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen style="border-radius:12px;max-width:100%;"></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience Section -->
    <section id="experience" class="profile-section">
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <div class="experience-items">
        {% for company in experience %}
        <div class="company-container">
          <div class="company-header">
            <h3 class="company-name">{{ company.company }}</h3>
            <p class="company-dates">{{ company.dates }}</p>
            <p class="exp-location">üìç {{ company.location if company.location else '' }}</p>
            <div class="exp-meta">
              <span class="exp-type">{{ company.type }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-item-container">
            {% if company.image %}
            <div class="company-logo">
              <img src="{{ company.image }}" alt="{{ company.company }} logo" />
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="company-info">
              {% if company.id == "blue-owl" %}
                <!-- Show overall summary and achievements once -->
                <div class="company-summary">
                  <p class="role-description">{{ company.roles[0].description }}</p>
                  <ul class="exp-roles">
                    {% for role in company.roles %}
                      <li><strong>{{ role.title }}</strong> <span>({{ role.dates }}, {{ role.duration }})</span></li>
                    {% endfor %}
                  </ul>
                  <div class="role-achievements">
                    <p class="achievements-title">Notable Achievements:</p>
                    <ul>
                      {% for achievement in company.roles[0].achievements %}
                        <li>{{ achievement }}</li>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {% else %}
                <!-- Default rendering for other companies -->
                {% for role in company.roles %}
                <div class="company-role">
                  <h4 class="role-title">{{ role.title }}</h4>
                  <p class="role-dates">{{ role.dates }} ¬∑ {{ role.duration }}</p>
                  {% if role.location %}
                  <p class="role-location">üìç {{ role.location }}</p>
                  {% endif %}
                  <p class="role-description">{{ role.description }}</p>
                  {% if role.achievements.length > 0 %}
                  <div class="role-achievements">
                    <p class="achievements-title">Notable Achievements:</p>
                    <ul>
                      {% for achievement in role.achievements %}
                      <li>{{ achievement }}</li>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <!-- Education Section -->
    <section id="education" class="profile-section">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <div class="education-items">
        {% for edu in education %}
        <div class="education-item">
          <div class="edu-header">
            <h3 class="edu-degree">{{ edu.degree }}</h3>
            <p class="edu-field">{{ edu.field }}</p>
          </div>
          <p class="edu-school">{{ edu.school }}</p>
          <p class="edu-dates">{{ edu.dates }}</p>
          {% if edu.activities.length > 0 %}
          <div class="edu-activities">
            <p class="activities-label">Activities and societies:</p>
            <div class="activities-list">
              {% for activity in edu.activities %}
              <span class="activity-badge">{{ activity }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Licenses & Certifications Section -->
    <section id="licenses" class="profile-section">
      <h2>Licenses & Certifications</h2>
      <div class="licenses-items">
        {% for cert in licenses %}
        <div class="license-item">
          <h3 class="cert-title">{{ cert.title }}</h3>
          <p class="cert-issuer">{{ cert.issuer }}</p>
          <p class="cert-date">Issued {{ cert.issuedDate }}</p>
          {% if cert.credentialId %}
          <p class="cert-id">Credential ID: {{ cert.credentialId }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="cert-skills">
            {% for skill in cert.skills %}
            <span class="skill-tag">{{ skill }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Volunteering Section -->
    <section id="volunteering" class="profile-section">
      <h2>Volunteering</h2>
      <div class="volunteering-items">
        {% for vol in volunteering %}
        <div class="volunteer-item">
          <div class="vol-header">
            <h3 class="vol-title">{{ vol.title }}</h3>
            <p class="vol-organization">{{ vol.organization }}</p>
          </div>
          <p class="vol-category">{{ vol.category }}</p>
          <p class="vol-dates">{{ vol.startDate }} - {{ vol.endDate }} ¬∑ {{ vol.duration }}</p>
          {% if vol.responsibilities.length > 0 %}
          <ul class="vol-responsibilities">
            {% for responsibility in vol.responsibilities %}
            <li>{{ responsibility }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Honors & Awards Section -->
    <section id="awards" class="profile-section">
      <h2>Honors & Awards</h2>
      <div class="awards-items">
        {% for award in awards %}
        <div class="award-item">
          <h3 class="award-title">{{ award.title }}</h3>
          <p class="award-issuer">Issued by {{ award.issuer }} ¬∑ {{ award.issuedDate }}</p>
          <p class="award-organization">{{ award.organization }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>
